OL,3,CJersey man handed 12 years in prison
OL,4,Cfor rape committed in 2002
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,7,Fthat some people may find distressing
OL,9,FA Jersey man who raped a teenager more
OL,10,Fthan two decades ago has been jailed
OL,11,Ffor 12 years.
OL,13,FSimon Paul De La Haye was sentenced at
OL,14,FJersey's Royal Court on Thursday 18
OL,15,FDecember 2025, but refused to attend
OL,16,Fhis sentencing either in person or via
OL,17,Fvideo link.
