OL,3,CJersey man handed 12 years in prison
OL,4,Cfor rape committed in 2002
OL,6,FIn his ruling, Bailiff Robert MacRae
OL,7,Falso handed De La Haye a lifetime
OL,8,Frestraining order and placed him on
OL,9,Fthe sex offenders list for 20 years.
OL,11,FThe court heard how De La Haye was in
OL,12,Fa short relationship with his victim
OL,13,Fin 2002 while she was a teenager and
OL,14,Fhe was in his 30s.
OL,16,FIn the same year, around 5 November,
OL,17,Fthe defendant raped the victim. This
OL,18,Fresulted in her falling pregnant but
OL,19,Fthen miscarrying the baby.
