OL,6,FThe victim also told the court that
OL,7,Fshe was in constant fear that someone
OL,8,Fwas lurking in her house and had to
OL,9,Fsleep with the television on to drown
OL,10,Fout outside noise.
OL,12,FIn 2023, the victim came forward to
OL,13,Ftell the States of Jersey Police what
OL,14,Fhad happened to her.
OL,16,FDe La Haye maintained he was innocent,
OL,17,Fbut following a trial in October this
OL,18,Fyear, a jury unanimously found him
OL,19,Fguilty after only a couple of hours of
OL,20,Fdeliberation.
