OL,6,FThe victim also told the court: "I
OL,7,Ffelt like I didn't deserve to be a
OL,8,Fmother, and I tried to end my life;
OL,9,Fluckily, my husband saved me. This is
OL,10,Fnever going to get better. The
OL,11,Faftermath is harrowing.
OL,13,F"At some point, every single day for
OL,14,F25 years, a memory of him has come
OL,15,Fback, and I have served a life
OL,16,Fsentence and always will."
