OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Alasdair Castle
OL,7,Ffrom the Criminal Investigations
OL,8,FDepartment said: "This conviction
OL,9,Fsends a clear message - survivors of
OL,10,Fsexual offences will be listened to,
OL,11,Fbelieved, and supported.
OL,13,F"I wish to personally thank the victim
OL,14,Ffor having the trust and confidence in
OL,15,Fus to investigate their case and
OL,16,Fremain patient throughout the criminal
OL,17,Fjustice process.
